originalText.text: Leila was TRULY a dream to work with. I am a wedding planner based in Boston and we worked closely together on a wedding in Vermont. Leila’s energy throughout the whole planning process made her just the best to work with. On the day of she was professional and calm and not to mention her photos are to die for. I keep scrolling through the album and it keeps getting better!! cannot recommend more.

originalText.text: There is no other way to describe Leila Brewster Photography without saying magical! Her photos are so magical and really capture the light and feelings of your special day. She is also just a really great person, outside of being a fantastic photographer -- super helpful, friendly, no ego, has an eye for detail and really leads you so you can get the best moment captured. Both my husband and I were so happy with the end results and our decision to go with Leila as our photographer. If she has availability for you, book her and don't even think twice about it!

originalText.text: Leila was our wedding photographer and went above and beyond in her service. She was so responsive, calm, and comforting throughout the planning process, which meant a lot to us. She was also able to do our engagement photos, rehearsal dinner and welcome party. All of her photos are outstanding and stunning. She captured our vision perfectly and we are so grateful she was our photographer.

originalText.text: We LOVE LOVE LOVE Leila & her work! Not only is she one of the coolest people on the planet, she is also an amazing photographer! My husband & I had such a wonderful experience with Leila on our destination wedding in Antigua, Guatemala. She was so easy to work with & captured the most beautiful details from the venue to the tiny moments that nobody thinks of capturing but end up making you relive that day. We just celebrated our 3 year wedding anniversary and going through our pictures made us feel so grateful for having had Leila on our team. She did such an amazing job & we have all these memories to relive thanks to her! Could not have had ANYBODY else for the job other than Leila!

originalText.text: Leila was absolutely incredible!  She shot our wedding in Fall 2019 and I would work with her again in a heartbeat.  The photos came out absolutely amazing, and she captured all of the incredible moments of the weekend.  She has such a calming presence and is so easy to work with, making people feel relaxed and themselves when taking photos. Would highly recommend working with Leila if you can!
